    <h1>Schedule a Pickup</h1>
    <p>Send a pickup request now, and we will be there for you!</p>
    <form class="schedule-pickup-form" action="/pickup" method="POST">
      <h2>Personal Details</h2>
      <label for="">Name</label><br/>
      <input class="name" type="text" name="name" placeholder="Your Name" required="required"/><br/>
      <label for="">Email</label><br/>
      <input class="email" type="email" name="email" placeholder="Your Email" required="required"/><br/>
      <label for="">Phone Number</label><br/>
      <input class="phone" type="text" name="tel" placeholder="Your Phone number" required="required"/><br/>

      <h2>Pickup Details</h2>
      <label for="">Date for pickup</label><br/>
      <input class="date_pickup" name="date" type="date" required="required"/><br/>
      <label for="">Estimated Time pickup</label><br/>
      <input class="time_pickup" name="time" type="time" min="09:00" max="20:00" required="required"/><br/>
      <label for="">Address for Pickup</label><br/>
      <textarea class="address_pickup" name="add" id="" cols="30" rows="3" placeholder="Your Address" required="required"></textarea><br/>
      <label for="">Anything more specific you'd want us to know?</label><br/>
      <textarea class="extra_notes" name="extra" id="" cols="30" rows="3" placeholder="Any details?" required="required"></textarea><br/>

      <h3>Recyclable Waste Details</h3>
      <label for="">Type of waste:
      </label><br/>
      <select name="typewst" input="input" class="waste_type" required="required">
        <option value="" disabled="disabled" selected="selected">Please select the type of waste majorly</option>
        <option value="paper">Paper (includes: old newspapers, magazines, used books, beverage & product cardboard cartons etc) + other stuff</option>
        <option value="Plastic">Plastic (includes: plastic bottles of all types, styrofoam products etc) + other stuff</option>
        <option value="Metal">Metal (includes: old utensils, cola cans, old metal parts of components etc) + other stuff</option>

      </select>

      <label for="">Estimate Quantity of waste:
      </label><br/>
      <select name="approxwt" input="input" class="quantity" required="required">
        <option value="" disabled="disabled" selected="selected">Please select an estimate range</option>
        <option value="1-5 kgs">1 - 5 kilograms</option>
        <option value="5-10 kgs">5 - 10 kilograms</option>
        <option value="above 10 kgs">Above 10 kilograms</option>

      </select>

      <button type="submit" value="Submit" id="pickup" onclick="myFunction()">Submit</button>
      
      </form>
      <h4>*Please note that while we assure our services to be in accordance with the above pickup time and pickup date provided by you, it however doesn't guarantee it. Pickup of your waste is subject to availability of our resources. Minimum delay of a
        day can be expected & you will be notified in advance by call.</h4>

    
